Firefox Memory Restart

Development
1. Create a text file called %USER-DIR%\Application Data\Mozilla\Firefox\Profiles\extensions\memoryrestart@teamextension.com or %USER-DIR%\AppData\Roaming\Mozilla\Firefox\Profiles\%RANDOM%.default\extensions\memoryrestart@teamextension.com".
2. Inside the text file, insert the text "C:\tex\dev\workspaces\teamextension\memoryrestart\".
3. For more information, see https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Building_an_Extension.

Deployment
1. Update version in build.properties and install.rdf.
2. Run ant.
3. Upload dist\memoryrestart-${version}-fx.xpi to https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/developers/addon/memory-restart/versions.

